{"tid":356624,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"性交轉運(冇性交圖)","createTime":"2017-08-12T08:45:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T06:44:53.000Z","uid":62067,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2354f1482f7a83c124579c5e6de2e8c737d3193","tid":356624,"uid":62067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:45:59.000Z","msg":"今年明明升市都賺唔到錢，決定用坊間流行嘅性交轉運大法即係叫雞提升運氣。<br />\n<br />\n睇圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/57fnwmxi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F57fnwmxi&h=dfc5d7e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我上晝買咗恒指牛證，唔夠一個鐘打咗靶。下晝未見回升跡像，臨收市買恒指牛證，翌日走去叫雞，我要用親身實驗睇吓性交可否轉運。星期一中午開估。<br />\n<br />\nP.S.: 雞已叫，波很大<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但腰也粗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，樣唔太差但又唔係好好"},{"pid":"09ae719e25e03abd31a7e626b383870c4b0e4ce5","tid":356624,"uid":78973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:49:48.000Z","msg":"未調整完喎"},{"pid":"1a7f6a1b4e6b76e9d6b8495497e23a874ad5671d","tid":356624,"uid":54481,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T09:14:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c5a2360e045ee075c0b63d3f1b062637cae2f3","tid":356624,"uid":129507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T09:58:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74d7e17fda133238315b737f4744b951f01ae49","tid":356624,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T09:59:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n🤣🤣"},{"pid":"8f01cf2fb2972f9596de2bd2d188e5e90a6a821f","tid":356624,"uid":24380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T13:22:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><